<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">About DataBuilderz</p>
        <h1>We help businesses turn fragmented data and inconsistent marketing into a scalable growth engine.</h1>
        <p class="lead">DataBuilderz was built for organizations that need more than channel execution. We bring together strategy, data operations, and measurable marketing delivery so revenue teams can move with confidence.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container split-grid">
        <div>
          <h2>Our perspective</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="stacked-copy">
          <p>Too many B2B teams run campaigns on incomplete data, siloed reporting, and generic messaging. The result is predictable: low response rates, rising acquisition costs, and wasted effort across sales and marketing.</p>
          <p>We built DataBuilderz to solve that gap. Our approach connects clean market data, audience insight, and practical digital marketing execution, helping clients improve targeting accuracy, campaign performance, and overall commercial efficiency.</p>
          <p>From emerging companies building visibility to established firms expanding into new markets, we support organizations that need sharper decisions and stronger demand generation systems.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section accent-band">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <p class="eyebrow">What we stand for</p>
          <h2>Principles that shape every engagement.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid three">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Accuracy First</h3>
            <p>Good strategy breaks quickly when the data is weak. We prioritize validation, relevance, and usability in every audience and dataset we build.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Execution Over Theory</h3>
            <p>We value plans that translate into campaigns, workflows, and measurable progress. Practical implementation matters more than presentation.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Partnership Mindset</h3>
            <p>We work as an extension of your team, aligning with your growth targets, operating rhythm, and internal stakeholders.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <p class="eyebrow">Who we serve</p>
          <h2>Built for businesses selling into diverse and data-sensitive markets.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid two">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Growth-Focused Marketing Teams</h3>
            <p>We support marketers who need dependable targeting, sharper segmentation, better content performance, and reporting that clearly maps to opportunity creation.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Sales and Revenue Operations Leaders</h3>
            <p>We help teams improve prospecting efficiency, enrich account intelligence, and create cleaner handoffs between campaign response and sales engagement.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section cta-section">
      <div class="container cta-box">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Let's build with intent</p>
          <h2>If your team needs stronger data foundations and a clearer route to market, we should talk.</h2>
        </div>
        <a class="button primary" href="/contact">Contact DataBuilderz</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/site.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
